title: Paige Comments After Nude Photos and Videos of WWE Star Leak on Twitter
text: Paige Comments After Nude Photos and Videos of WWE Star Leak on Twitter Ian Gavan/Getty Images Mike Chiari Featured Columnist March 17, 2017 WWE Superstar Paige released a statement on Twitter after the leak of nude photos and videos involving her Friday. Paige said the following with regard to the controversy: PAIGE @RealPaigeWWE Personal and private photos of mine were stolen and unfortunately they were shared publicly without my consent. 3/17/2017, 11:16:42 PM According to Raj Giri of WrestlingInc.com, Paige was reportedly hacked. The 24-year-old native of England has been part of WWE's main roster since 2014 when she debuted and defeated AJ Lee for the Divas Championship in her first match. She hasn't wrestled since June, however, due to a neck injury . Part of the famous Knight wrestling family, Paige has competed since the age of 13 and is a two-time Divas champion as well as the inaugural NXT Women's champion. Like the new article format? !
